OL,3,CReeves to extend benefit fraud
OL,4,Ccrackdown in Budget
OL,6,FRachel Reeves will extend a crackdown
OL,7,Fon benefit fraud in a bid to raise
OL,8,F#1.2 billion as she seeks to balance
OL,9,Fthe books in the Budget this week.
OL,11,FIt comes as she is expected to scrap
OL,12,Fthe two-child benefit cap, in a move
OL,13,Fthat could cost more than #3 billion.
OL,15,FThe Chancellor is also thought to be
OL,16,Fpoised to raise taxes in an effort to
OL,17,Fbridge a multibillion-pound gap in her
OL,18,Fspending plans.
