OL,3,CReeves to extend benefit fraud
OL,4,Ccrackdown in Budget
OL,6,FShe will extending targeted case
OL,7,Freviews, which root out inaccuracies
OL,8,Fin universal credit claims, with the
OL,9,Faim of bringing in an extra #1.2
OL,10,Fbillion by March 2031.
OL,12,FShe could also hit more than 100,000
OL,13,Fhigh-value properties with a levy that
OL,14,Fapplies to those worth more than #2
OL,15,Fmillion and could raise #400-#450
OL,16,Fmillion, The Times reported.
OL,18,FSome 2.4 million properties in the top
OL,19,Fthree council tax bands would be
OL,20,Frevalued to determine which would be
OL,21,Fsubject to the surcharge.
