OL,6,FPeople will be able to defer the cost
OL,7,Funtil they die or move house to avoid
OL,8,Fforcing them to sell up, according to
OL,9,Fthe newspaper.
OL,11,FMs Reeves is grappling with weak
OL,12,Feconomic growth, persistent inflation
OL,13,Fand an expected downgrade to official
OL,14,Fproductivity forecasts as she prepares
OL,15,Fher statement.
OL,17,FAfter scrapping plans to raise income
OL,18,Ftax, she is expected to look to a
OL,19,F"smorgasbord" of smaller measures to
OL,20,Fbring in cash.
