OL,3,CReeves to extend benefit fraud
OL,4,Ccrackdown in Budget
OL,6,FShe is thought to be considering
OL,7,Fbringing in a pay-per-mile tax for
OL,8,Felectric vehicle drivers and limiting
OL,9,Fhow much workers can stash in their
OL,10,Fpensions under salary sacrifice
OL,11,Fschemes before paying national
OL,12,Finsurance.
OL,14,FAnd she will reaffirm the Government's
OL,15,Fcommitment to the triple lock on state
OL,16,Fpensions, and confirm that 13 million
OL,17,Fpensioners are set to benefit from an
OL,18,Fabove inflation rise next April.
