OL,3,CReeves to extend benefit fraud
OL,4,Ccrackdown in Budget
OL,6,FAn extension of the freeze on income
OL,7,Ftax thresholds is also among rumoured
OL,8,Fmeasures and would see more people
OL,9,Fdragged into paying tax for the first
OL,10,Ftime or shifted into a higher rate as
OL,11,Ftheir wages go up.
OL,13,FThe Lib Dems have said the move would
OL,14,Fbe "rank hypocrisy" and amount to a
OL,15,F"stealth tax stitch-up" by Labour and
OL,16,Fthe Conservatives.
