OL,3,CReeves to extend benefit fraud
OL,4,Ccrackdown in Budget
OL,6,FThey say extending it for two years
OL,7,Fwill drag another 1.3 million into
OL,8,Fstarting to pay income tax or into the
OL,9,Fhigher rate, on top of 7.7 million
OL,10,Falready estimated to be hit under the
OL,11,FConservative freeze due to end in 2028.
OL,13,FLib Dem deputy leader Daisy Cooper
OL,14,Fsaid: "A staggering nine million
OL,15,Fpeople are now set to be hit by the
OL,16,FConservative`Labour stealth tax stitch-
OL,17,Fup."
OL,19,FShe added: "Families across the
OL,20,Fcountry are fed up with being milked
OL,21,Ffor their hard-earned cash."
